<A HREF="http://fohguild.org/news/STAMPEDE.jpg"><img src=http://fohguild.org/news/STAMPEDE.jpg border=0 width=400 height=300></A><br />
<br />
All I know is this; after the Plane of Tactics, this whole expansion is going to be a huge letdown.<br />
<br />
You take a zone. YOU TAKE THE DAMN ZONE I SAY. You fill up the zone with (1) Ogres to kill... endless masses of Ogres... Ogre after Ogre after Ogre... then more Ogres (2) You add Boars. BOARS! FFS BOARS!! (3) S-T-A-M-P-E-D-E of BOARS. BOARS!!! WILD STAMPEDING BOARS. I SHIT YOU NOT! (4) An Ogre that quad rampages for 7,000 damage. Yes, 7,000! (5) BOARS! (6) Cool ass quests and mini-events and ring events and whatever... (7) OGRES TO KILL! <br />
<br />
I only leave you with this piece of advice. Should you hear the emote of Thundering Hooves - GET THE FUCK OUT OF THE WAY OF THE STAMPEDING BOARS. I pay so you don't have to... <br />
<br />
